The presentation layer manages UI and state management (Cubit) codes. It includes cubit, pages, and widgets folders. Moreover, a presentation.dart file exports the presentation layer codes. Cubits and widgets within this layer may be shared across multiple pages within a module. However, if a cubit or widget is exclusive to a single page, it may be placed in its dedicated page folder (e.g., pages/login/widgets/login_button.dart, pages/login/cubit/login_cubit.dart).
